T1  - The sensitivity of bank stock returns to market, interest and exchange rate risks
AU  - Choi, Jongmoo Jay
AU  - Elyasiani, Elyas
AU  - Kopecky, Kenneth J.
JO  - Journal of Banking & Finance
VL  - 16
IS  - 5
SP  - 983
